Package com.quackology.duckdevices.spaces

Class MatReal

java.lang.Object
com.quackology.duckdevices.spaces.MatReal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Linear, Mat<MatReal>, Space
public class MatReal extends Object implements Mat<MatReal>
Wrapper class for 2D matrix of real numbers

Based on OjAlgo's PrimitiveMatrix interface (MatrixR064)
